            <title><![CDATA[Grinding Gear Games Sets Reveal Details for Path of Exile 2's Huge Return of the Ancients Update]]></title>
            <link>https://www.mmorpg.com/news/grinding-gear-games-sets-reveal-details-for-path-of-exile-2s-huge-return-of-the-ancients-update-2000137893</link>
            <guid>1501105</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p><span>Grinding Gear Games is getting close to revealing all about <a href="https://www.mmorpg.com/path-of-exile-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Path of Exile 2’</em></a>s next big content update, Return of the Ancients.</span></p>

                
                    
                        

		
		
		
		
		
		
				
		
		

		

		
		
		
		
		
		
		
                    
                
            
<p><span>The next Grinding Gear Games live is happening on May 7th, and the team includes an announcement teaser to tide us over for now. The previously teased as <a href="https://www.mmorpg.com/news/path-of-exile-2-offers-a-window-for-their-huge-050-update-reveals-2000137331" target="_blank" rel="noopener">huge 0.5.0 update</a>&nbsp;launch&nbsp; is coming on May 29th at 1:00 p.m. PDT on PC and console.&nbsp; before then though, we'll find out everything on May 7th when the stream happens <a href="https://www.pathofexile.com/forum/view-thread/3929238" target="_blank" rel="noopener">at 1:00 p.m. Pacific / 4:00 p.m. Eastern on Twitch.</a></span></p>
<p><span><iframe width="560" height="314" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/tqb4pk3bkbs"></iframe></span></p>
<p><span>As usual, the GGG team will detail everything coming in the major update, which they’re teasing with “ancient secrets rise”. The teaser hints at all that nicely. There is a giant fortress, giant enough to span continents, suddenly in Wraeclast. It’s full of secrets. And challenges. And more that we’ll find out about that’s to be revealed behind its walls.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span>Expect to learn about the narrative content on the way, endgame revamps, likely item details, and more. There will be Twitch Drops for tuning in, which will be revealed closer to the stream date.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span>After the big reveals, once again, we’ll get a community Q&amp;A with ZiggyD, Jonathan, and Mark answering what they can on everything they’ve just revealed and more beyond.</span></p>

                
                    
                        

		
		
		
		
		
		
				
		
		

		

		
		
		
		
		
		
		
                    
                
            
</div></div><br/><br/>https://www.mmorpg.com/news/grinding-gear-games-sets-reveal-details-for-path-of-exile-2s-huge-return-of-the-ancients-update-2000137893]]></content:encoded>
